<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺超棒的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想之後或許還會受你照顧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然都是同一座島上的居民，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就讓我們互相幫助吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唷，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />
