	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了答謝你幫我找住處，<delay20 />
你就收下這個
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的<colour id="1" />方程式<colour id="65535" />吧！</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛來到這座島時，<delay20 />
我看到整片滿滿的雜草，<delay20 />
就想到用雜草來<colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ<colour id="65535" />哩！</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你沒做過<colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ<colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />好像可以教你，<delay8 />
你可以先去<colour id="1" />服務處<colour id="65535" />看看喔！</message>
	<message label="003_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是雜草，<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />換個角度看，
