我們就好好活用它吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你幫我找住處，我得給你謝禮才行呢。<delay frames="30" />
