	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />那把傘<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會是用我給的方程式<delay20 />
