<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挺不錯的吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正好適合雨天散步時用吧？<delay40 />
